306
00:22:46.472 --> 00:22:47.639
Ta là...

307
00:22:49.641 --> 00:22:50.809
Spot.

308
00:22:51.477 --> 00:22:53.145
Ta lại gặp nhau, Spider
-Man.

309
00:22:55.731 --> 00:22:57.941
